ditional experts available for consultation&lt;/div>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/tbody>&lt;/table>&lt;div aria-live="polite" class="hwp-visually-hidden" id="sort-note">&lt;/div>&lt;/div>&lt;h2>Harvard Research Support&lt;/h2>&lt;span id="sort-hint" style="display:none;">Sort&lt;/span>&lt;div class="hwp-table-wrap">&lt;table class="hwp-table js-hwp-table dataTable">&lt;thead>&lt;tr>&lt;th>Resources Link&lt;/th>&lt;th>Description&lt;/th>&lt;/tr>&lt;/thead>&lt;tbody>&lt;tr>&lt;td data-title="Resources Link">&lt;div class="hwp-table__cell-content">&lt;a class="hwp-link" href="https://rc.fas.harvard.edu/">FAS Research Computing&lt;/a>&lt;/div>&lt;/td>&lt;td data-title="Description">&lt;div class="hwp-table__cell-content">Computing cluster, support and training funded by FAS.&lt;/div>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;tr>&lt;td data-title="Resources Link">&lt;div class="hwp-table__cell-content">&lt;a class="hwp-link" href="https://www.hbs.edu/research-computing-services/about-us/statistical-and-data-services.aspx">Research Computing Services, Harvard Business School&lt;/a>&lt;/div>&lt;/td>&lt;td data-title="Description">&lt;div class="hwp-table__cell-content">Support for statistical analysis and computing, research software training for HBS researchers.&lt;/div>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;tr>&lt;td data-title="Resources Link">&lt;div class="hwp-table__cell-content">&lt;a class="hwp-link" href="http://its.gse.harvard.edu/services/research">Research Support Services, Harvard Graduate School of Education&lt;/a>&lt;/div>&lt;/td>&lt;td data-title="Description">&lt;div class="hwp-table__cell-content">Research software training (e.g., R, Stata, Mplus, NVivo, Atlas.ti) and consulting services at HGSE.&lt;/div>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;tr>&lt;td data-title="Resources Link">&lt;div class="hwp-table__cell-content">&lt;a class="hwp-link" href="https://digitalhumanities.fas.harvard.edu/">Digital Arts &amp;amp; Humanities at Harvard University&lt;/a>&lt;/div>&lt;/td>&lt;td data-title="Description">&lt;div class="hwp-table